\v 18 I said/thought \add to myself\add*, “I am ◄falling/about to die►,”
\q2 but Yahweh, you held me up by faithfully loving me.
\q1
\v 19 Whenever I am very worried,
\q2 you comfort/encourage me and cause me to be happy.
