\q1
\v 20 You have nothing to do with wicked judges,
\q2 who establish laws that allow people to do what is not legal.
\q1
\v 21 They plan to get rid of righteous people,
\q1 and they declare that ◄innocent people/people who have not done what is wrong► must be executed.
\q1
